12. On or about September 23, 2021, the owners provided the lienor with a
punch list of items to be completed. This list was itemized and responded to by the
lienor on September 23, 2021.
13. On November 8, 2021, the lienor communicated with the owner to
schedule a time to continue a portion of the outstanding punch list.
14. The last time the lienor performed work on the property was November
9, 2021.
15. On November 30, 2021, the lienor provided a final invoice in the amount
of $9,136.16 to the owners for work and materials completed.
16. On December 3, 2021, the owner made a refusal to pay the outstanding
balance.
17.
Nine thousand one hundred thirty-six dollars and sixteen cents remain
. unpaid for the labor performed and material furnished, and the lienor claims a lien for
that amount.
18.
The total amount for which lien is being filed for is $9,136.16.
19.
The property subject to the lien is situated in the County of Schoharie,
Town of Blenheim, at Lot Number: 10; Block: 1; Subdivision: 170 .; Tax Map Number:
170 .- 1-10 and Deed Reference Number: Book 690 Page 182.
